data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home and experience the best of Summerset living. This home is a four bedroom, three bath, two car garage within a quiet neighborhood with landscaping and a fenced back yard. With three levels to live in, it provides room for privacy and yet enough room to accompany most arrangements with living space. Come view this home and let us know what you think!
